{"id": "1440733058411008062", "channel_id": "1426837316533747823", "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "content": "While our work may seem like a Lovecraftian tribute, what we’ve always sought to express is a theme entirely antithetical to cosmic nihilism —— our gameplay experience, story, art, music, development journey, and the community itself all embody this. I love you all, Keepers. I love you all, members of the B.I.A.V.Studio.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T15:58:48.651000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 55}, {"emoji": "love", "emoji_id": "1356053099931897977", "count": 10}]}
{"id": "1440735248391475240", "channel_id": "1426837316533747823", "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "content": "我们虽然看起来所做的是一个Lovecraft致敬的作品，实际上我们要表达的始终是与宇宙虚无主义完全对立的课题———我们的游戏体验、我们的故事美术与音乐、我们的研发历程、我们的社区本身都是其体现。我爱你们，所有的守密人。我爱你们，所有的脑缸组成员。", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T16:07:30.783000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 13}]}
